{"tid":542343,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩八達通寄咗封信話我遺失咗張卡叫我去拎返啲餘額","createTime":"2018-01-27T11:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T13:33:38.000Z","uid":98507,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4c78affab23796dbd1f272b49ad858d5155e5009","tid":542343,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:19:40.000Z","msg":"對上一次唔見都唔知係幾時嘅事<br />\n而家用緊嗰張係馬年版 14年出<br />\n呢4年我都冇用過其他卡<br />\n所以對上一次唔見至少係4年前<br />\n而且寄得信畀我應該係個人八達通<br />\n如果冇記錯應該唔見超過6年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係佢話有人執到我張卡 咁照計唔係有得拎返張卡架咩<br />\n而家直接退錢比我唔知做乜鳩<br />\n好撚詭異<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25eef06d7e1fa705ca10f517f0f5358dc8ad3e6","tid":542343,"uid":89953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:21:27.000Z","msg":"我之前都試過好似巴打你咁"},{"pid":"a431bd23b3a3fa5e906751be584a6782950820a7","tid":542343,"uid":98507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b25eef06d7e1fa705ca10f517f0f5358dc8ad3e6","tid":542343,"uid":89953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:21:27.000Z","msg":"我之前都試過好似巴打你咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:53:38.000Z","msg":"咁真係你唔見左定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無理由隔左咁耐先比人執到"},{"pid":"1408b850092607860fe62375d2b31a221440a2e0","tid":542343,"uid":89953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a431bd23b3a3fa5e906751be584a6782950820a7","tid":542343,"uid":98507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b25eef06d7e1fa705ca10f517f0f5358dc8ad3e6","tid":542343,"uid":89953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:21:27.000Z","msg":"我之前都試過好似巴打你咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:53:38.000Z","msg":"咁真係你唔見左定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無理由隔左咁耐先比人執到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T12:38:48.000Z","msg":"我個情況係6 7年前搭車整唔見咗張學生八達通，之後都補拎咗張新嘅一直用。然後突然收到通知叫我去拎返6 7 年前張八達通嘅